Package: IMBUS
Type: Package
Title: IMBUS: Implementing More and Better Use of ICES Survey Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("IMBUS", "Project", email = "imbus@ices.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Consolidates and extends useful functions from FLRebuild, FLCore, 
    and icesdata for IMBUS T4.4: Assessment of Survey-based Indices. Includes 
    spatial indicator functions (spreadingarea, gini, positivearea, proppres, 
    equivalentarea, densitylevel, spi, extentofoccurrence). Provides 
    standardized workflows for survey index calculation, length-based indicators, 
    auxiliary data extraction, and validation tools.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    FLCore (>= 2.6.0),
    FLRebuild (>= 0.1.0),
    icesdata (>= 0.1.0)
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
URL: https://github.com/laurieKell/IMBUS
BugReports: https://github.com/laurieKell/IMBUS/issues
